connectivity, (ii)\n$k$-edge-connectivity and (iii) the property of minimum vertex degree being at\nleast $k$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Sep 2014 17:48:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Nov 2014 06:55:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-19"}
