ase of the equilibration time of the complex upon increase\nof the interaction strength between DNA and the surface is ascribable to the\nassociated decrease of the probability to form new bridges between DNA and the\nproteins.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Sep 2014 09:09:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-23"}
